stures. At night, one of the canisters crash-lands in George's habitat, and George is exposed to the pathogen..</p>","tmdb_id":427641,"cast":["Dwayne Johnson","Naomie Harris","Malin Åkerman","Jeffrey Dean Morgan","Jake Lacy","Joe Manganiello","Marley Shelton","P.J. Byrne","Demetrius Grosse","Jack Quaid","Breanne Hill","Matt Gerald","Will Yun Lee","Urijah Faber","Bruce Blackshear"],"director":["Brad Peyton"],"keywords":["monster","wolf","mutation","gorilla","giant monster","lizard","giant lizard","creature","based on video game","giant animal","mutant animal","kaiju","albino","giant","rat","genetic experiment","destroyed city","giant gorilla","animal monster"],"tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"427641","season":null,"vote_average":6.451,"vote_count":7390},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Dwayne Johnson","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Dwayne Johnson","tmdb_id":18918,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5QApZVV8FUFlVxQpIK3Ew6cqotq.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/18918"},{"name":"Naomie Harris","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Naomie Harris","tmdb_id":2038,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/41TVAcYqKKF7PGf3x7QfaLvkLSW.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2038"},{"name":"Malin Åkerman","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Malin Åkerman","tmdb_id":50463,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/u38qRcCAiO3SZdFKJKx3fncDyef.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/50463"},{"name":"Jeffrey Dean Morgan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jeffrey Dean Morgan","tmdb_id":47296,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m8bdrmh6ExDCGQ64E83mHg002YV.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/47296"},{"name":"Jake Lacy","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jake Lacy","tmdb_id":496470,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qU6n9EaesBGqhNLlj5BecUrb5LW.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/496470"},{"name":"Joe Manganiello","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Joe Manganiello","tmdb_id":20580,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mTd